name: CoolCoin
description: Deep within the radioactive core of planet Wallstreet Wasteland… a mysterious and powerful force was born - The Cool Coin. This extraordinary gold coin, forged from the essence of an ancient supernova, holds the key to the very fabric of Coolman’s Universe. For eons, civilizations have whispered tales of Cool Coin’s unimaginable power and the destiny of those who seek to harness it…
